      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the most exacting standards. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a life of meticulous climate-controlled storage and preventative care. For the discerning collector or professional seeking an uncompromised driving experience, this motorcar represents the pinnacle of its class. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior, adheres to original factory specifications. Serious inquiries only.",
