      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be passing along this absolute gem. Honestly, you'd think it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014it's that perfect! I've taken such good care of it, and it still has that fresh new-car smell. No scratches, no dents, just pure driving bliss waiting for its next home. You really have to see it in person to believe how gorgeous it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
