    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, an analog masterpiece featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a reinforced rear subframe, comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and recent rod bearing prophylaxis. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis maintains its original rigidity, with all suspension bushings and dampers performing to factory specifications. A true turn-key enthusiast vehicle with impeccable mechanical provenance.",
