      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This vehicle is in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections; it looks as though it just rolled off the assembly line. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every tactile surface\u2014from the hand-stitched steering wheel to the dampened switchgear\u2014feels crisp and unused. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, document-backed service history with every maintenance milestone performed ahead of schedule. This is a rare opportunity to own a 'time capsule' vehicle that performs exactly as the engineers intended. All original keys, factory manuals, and a bespoke car cover are included in the sale.",
